    "description": "Sans Logique is a puzzle/adventure game set in a strange, fantastical world. Through the eyes of a mysterious character, you'll have to solve riddles to find your way out, venturing ever deeper into this world mixing dream and reality. You'll have to find your way out of this labyrinth, first with your hands and then with the help of various objects that will give you powers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Puzzles</strong></h2>Solve a variety of original riddles to unravel the mysteries of Sans Logique and understand your story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/2d54fc1962233acc3da074b593c6bb0f.poster.avif?t=1696622400\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/2d54fc1962233acc3da074b593c6bb0f.webm?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/2d54fc1962233acc3da074b593c6bb0f.mp4?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploration</strong></h2>Travel through strange portals and discover the different dream worlds inhabited by strange beings that make up Sans Logique. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/a93ee5ff560bacad050e50da533322ea.poster.avif?t=1696622400\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/a93ee5ff560bacad050e50da533322ea.webm?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/a93ee5ff560bacad050e50da533322ea.mp4?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Infiltration </strong></h2>Escape your fears, the shadows, those terrible monsters that roam the caves, by adopting the strategy that suits you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/84ea350012533d81278f648d7c3706eb.poster.avif?t=1696622400\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/84ea350012533d81278f648d7c3706eb.webm?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/84ea350012533d81278f648d7c3706eb.mp4?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interactions </strong></h2>Use the various powers you'll find along the way to solve puzzles and advance through the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/96cdbee6828a2d7874d704f570830b8b.poster.avif?t=1696622400\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/96cdbee6828a2d7874d704f570830b8b.webm?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837620/extras/96cdbee6828a2d7874d704f570830b8b.mp4?t=1696622400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
